android.car.vms

类 VmsSubscriberManager

  • java.lang.Object
    • android.car.CarManagerBase
      • android.car.vms.VmsSubscriberManager
  • 已过时。 
    Use VmsClientManager instead

    @Deprecated
public final class VmsSubscriberManager
extends CarManagerBase
    API implementation for use by Vehicle Map Service subscribers. Supports a single client callback that can subscribe and unsubscribe to different data layers. setVmsSubscriberClientCallback(java.util.concurrent.Executor, android.car.vms.VmsSubscriberManager.VmsSubscriberClientCallback) must be called before any subscription operations.

      • onCarDisconnected

        public void onCarDisconnected()
        已过时。 
        从类复制的说明: CarManagerBase
        Handle disconnection of car service (=crash). As car service has crashed already, this call should only clean up any listeners / callbacks passed from client. Clearing object passed to car service is not necessary as car service has crashed. Note that Car*Manager will not work any more as all binders are invalid. Client should re-create all Car*Managers when car service is restarted.
        指定者:
        onCarDisconnected 在类中 CarManagerBase
